{{#*inline "title"}}Prompt Set Started! | Twennie{{/inline}}

<div class="success-container">
  <h1 class="success-title">You're all set to begin!</h1>

  <p class="success-message">
    You've successfully registered for the prompt set: <strong>{{promptSetTitle}}</strong>.
  </p>

  <p class="success-message">
    This set is designed to be completed <strong>{{frequency}}</strong>. Your target completion date is <strong>{{targetCompletionDate}}</strong>.
  </p>

  <p class="success-message">
    To stay on track, aim to complete each prompt by its recommended date. You'll find your prompts listed under the "Registered Prompt Sets" tab on your dashboard.
  </p>

  <p class="success-message">
    For each prompt:
  </p>
  <ul class="success-list">
    <li>Read the prompt carefully.</li>
    <li>Engage with the activity or reflection it suggests.</li>
    <li>Record your thoughts or findings in the provided notes section.</li>
    <li>Click "submit this prompt" to save your entry.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="success-message">
    Upon completing all prompts in the set, you'll earn the <strong>{{badgeName}}</strong> badge!
  </p>

  <div class="success-badge-display">
    <img src="{{badgeImage}}" alt="{{badgeName}} badge" style="height: 100px; margin-top: 1rem;">
  </div>

  <a href="{{dashboard}}" class="success-button">return to my dashboard</a>
</div>

